pe\" class=\"gt_row gt_left\">Expert assessment</td>\n<td headers=\"Fairness and impartiality  proxy\" class=\"gt_row gt_left\">Yes</td>\n<td headers=\"Fairness and impartiality  transform\" class=\"gt_row gt_left\">None</td>\n<td headers=\"Fairness and impartiality  wt_intheme\" class=\"gt_row gt_center\">50.0%</td>\n<td headers=\"Fairness and impartiality  wt_theme\" class=\"gt_row gt_center\">12.5%</td>\n<td headers=\"Fairness and impartiality  wt_total\" class=\"gt_row gt_center\">6.2%</td>\n<td headers=\"Fairness and impartiality  source_definition\" class=\"gt_row gt_left\">Generally speaking, how often would you say that public sector employees today, in your chosen country, act impartially when deciding how to implement a policy in an individual case? [Rated 1-7; mean score]</td></tr>\n    <tr class=\"gt_group_heading_row\">\n      <th colspan=\"9\" class=\"gt_group_heading\" scope=\"colgroup\" id=\"Adherence to rules/procedures\">Adherence to rules/procedures</th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"gt_row_group_first\"><td headers=\"Adherence to rules/procedures  label\" class=\"gt_row gt_left\">Officials follow rules</td>\n<td headers=\"Adherence to rules/procedures  source_out\" class=\"gt_row gt_center\">QoG</td>\n<td headers=\"Adherence to rules/procedures  type\" class=\"gt_row gt_left\">Expert assessment</td>\n<td headers=\"Adherence to rules/procedures  proxy\" class=\"gt_row gt_left\">Yes</td>\n<td headers=\"Adherence to rules/procedures  transform\" class=\"gt_row gt_left\">None</td>\n<td headers=\"Adherence to rules/procedures  wt_intheme\" class=\"gt_row gt_center\">50.0%</td>\n<td headers=\"Adherence to rules/procedures  wt_theme\" class=\"gt_row gt_center\">12.5%</td>\n<td headers=\"Adherence to rules/procedures  wt_total\" class=\"gt_row gt_center\">6.2%</td>\n<td headers=\"Adherence to rules/procedures  source_definition\" class=\"gt_row gt_left\">Public sector employees strive to follow rules [Rated 1-7; mean score]</td></tr>\n    <tr><td headers=\