citizens  wt_total\" class=\"gt_row gt_center\">4.2%</td>\n<td headers=\"Serving government and citizens  source_definition\" class=\"gt_row gt_left\">Public sector employees strive to fulfill the ideology of the party/parties in government [Rated 1-7; mean score]</td></tr>\n    <tr class=\"gt_group_heading_row\">\n      <th colspan=\"9\" class=\"gt_group_heading\" scope=\"colgroup\" id=\"Work ethic\">Work ethic</th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"gt_row_group_first\"><td headers=\"Work ethic  label\" class=\"gt_row gt_left\">Unathorised absence</td>\n<td headers=\"Work ethic  source_out\" class=\"gt_row gt_center\">QoG</td>\n<td headers=\"Work ethic  type\" class=\"gt_row gt_left\">Expert assessment</td>\n<td headers=\"Work ethic  proxy\" class=\"gt_row gt_left\">Yes</td>\n<td headers=\"Work ethic  transform\" class=\"gt_row gt_left\">Inverted</td>\n<td headers=\"Work ethic  wt_intheme\" class=\"gt_row gt_center\">50.0%</td>\n<td headers=\"Work ethic  wt_theme\" class=\"gt_row gt_center\">12.5%</td>\n<td headers=\"Work ethic  wt_total\" class=\"gt_row gt_center\">6.2%</td>\n<td headers=\"Work ethic  source_definition\" class=\"gt_row gt_left\">Public employees are absent from work with- out permission [Rated 1-7; mean score]</td></tr>\n    <tr><td headers=\"Work ethic  label\" class=\"gt_row gt_left\">Officials strive to be efficient</td>\n<td headers=\"Work ethic  source_out\" class=\"gt_row gt_center\">QoG</td>\n<td headers=\"Work ethic  type\" class=\"gt_row gt_left\">Expert assessment</td>\n<td headers=\"Work ethic  proxy\" class=\"gt_row gt_left\">Yes</td>\n<td headers=\"Work ethic  transform\" class=\"gt_row gt_left\">None</td>\n<td headers=\"Work ethic  wt_intheme\" class=\"gt_row gt_center\">50.0%</td>\n<td headers=\"Work ethic  wt_theme\" class=\"gt_row gt_center\">12.5%</td>\n<td headers=\"Work ethic  wt_total\" class=\"gt_row gt_center\">6.2%</td>\n<td headers=\"Work ethic  source_definition\" class=\"gt_row gt_left\">Public sector employees strive to be ef